Alembic migrations for Syntexa.

Generate a new revision from model changes:
    alembic -c syntexa/alembic.ini revision --autogenerate -m "describe change"

Apply to the configured database:
    alembic -c syntexa/alembic.ini upgrade head

The database URL is resolved from SYNTEXA_DATABASE_URL (see syntexa/config/settings.py).
